&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://trains.techpawz.com/posts/paris-to-nice/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Nice&lt;/a&gt;, located on the stunning French Riviera, is a vibrant city that beautifully blends old-world charm with modern sophistication. Known for its sun-kissed beaches, azure waters, and a rich cultural heritage, Nice offers visitors a delightful mix of relaxation and exploration. The Promenade des Anglais, a picturesque waterfront boulevard, invites you to stroll alongside the Mediterranean, while the historic Old Town (Vieux Nice) enchants with its narrow, winding streets and colorful buildings.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Paris Michelin Restaurant Guide</title><link>https://michelin.techpawz.com/posts/michelin-restaurants-paris/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 22:51:04 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://michelin.techpawz.com/posts/michelin-restaurants-paris/</guid><description>&lt;script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-8772455780561463"
